        <div n="Y03-315A">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-Y03-315A-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y03-315A-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y03-315A-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-Y03-315A-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y03-315A-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y03-315A-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-Y03-315A-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y03-315A-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y03-315A-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="italics">1</hi><lb/>The Life of Man to represent,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-2" n="2">And turn it all to ridicule;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-3" n="3">Wit did a Poppit Show invent,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-4" n="4">Where the chief Actor is a Fool.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-5" n="5"><hi rend="italics">2</hi><lb/>The Gods of old were Logs of Wood,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-6" n="6">And worship was to Poppits pay'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-7" n="7">In antick dress the Idol stood,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-8" n="8">And Priests &amp; People bow'd the head.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-9" n="9"><hi rend="italics">3</hi><lb/>No wonder than if Art began</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-10" n="10">The simple Votaries to frame;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-11" n="11">To shape in Timber foolish Man,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-12" n="12">And consecrate the Block to Fame.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-13" n="13"><hi rend="italics">4</hi><lb/>From hence Poetick fancy learn'd</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-14" n="14">That Trees might rise from human Forms,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-15" n="15">The Body to a Trunk be turn'd,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-16" n="16">And branches issue from the arms.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-17" n="17"><hi rend="italics">5</hi><lb/>Thus Dabalus <note place="foot">路two famous Writers.</note>  Ovid too</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-18" n="18">That Man's a Blockhead have confest,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-19" n="19">Powel <note place="foot">路two famous Masters of Poppit Shows.</note>  Stretch the hint pursue,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-20" n="20">Life is a Farce, the World a Iest.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-21" n="21"><hi rend="italics">6</hi><lb/>The same \<hi rend="italics">add</hi>路great\ truth South Sea has prov'd,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-22" n="22">On that damn'd Theatre the Alley,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-23" n="23">Where thousands by Directors mov'd</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-24" n="24">Are now sad monuments of Folly.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-25" n="25"><hi rend="italics">7</hi><lb/>What Momus was of old to Iove,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-26" n="26">The same a Harlequin is now,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-27" n="27">The former was buffoon'd above,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-28" n="28">The latter is a Punch below.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-29" n="29"><hi rend="italics">8</hi><lb/>This fleeting Scene is but a Stage,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-30" n="30">Where various images appear,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-31" n="31">In different parts of youth &amp; age,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-32" n="32">Alike the Prince &amp; Peasant share.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-33" n="33"><hi rend="italics">9</hi><lb/>Some draw our eyes by being great,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-34" n="34">False Pomp conceals mere wood within,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-35" n="35">And Legislators rang'd in state</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-36" n="36">Are oft but Wisdom in Machine.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-37" n="37"><hi rend="italics">10</hi><lb/>A Stock may chance to wear a Crown,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-38" n="38">And Timber, as a Lord, take place,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-39" n="39">A Statue may put on a Frown,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-40" n="40">And cheat us with a thinking face.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-41" n="41"><hi rend="italics">11</hi><lb/>Others are blindly led away,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-42" n="42">And made to act for ends unknown,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-43" n="43">By the mere spring of Wits they play,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-44" n="44">And speak in language not their own.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-45" n="45"><hi rend="italics">12</hi><lb/>Too oft, alass! a scolding Wife</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-46" n="46">Usurps a jolly Fellow's throne,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-47" n="47">And many drink the Cup of Life,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-48" n="48">Mix'd &amp; embitter'd by a Ione.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-49" n="49"><hi rend="italics">13</hi><lb/>In short, whatever men pursue</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-50" n="50">Of pleasure, folly, or of Love,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-51" n="51">This mimick路race brings all to view,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-52" n="52">Alike they dress, they talk, they move.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-53" n="53"><hi rend="italics">14</hi><lb/>Go on, great Stretch, with artfull hand</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-54" n="54">Mortals to please, &amp; to deride,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-55" n="55">And when Death breaks thy vital Band,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-56" n="56">Thou shalt put on the Poppit's pride.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-57" n="57"><hi rend="italics">15</hi><lb/>Thou shalt in Puny wood be shewn,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-58" n="58">Thy image shall preserve thy fame,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-59" n="59">Ages to come thy worth shall own,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-60" n="60">Point at thy limbs, &amp; tell thy name.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-61" n="61"><hi rend="italics">16</hi><lb/>Tell Tom he draws a farce in vain,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-62" n="62">Before he looks in Nature's glass,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-63" n="63">Punns cannot form a witty scene,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-64" n="64">Nor Pageantry for Honour pass.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-65" n="65"><hi rend="italics">17</hi><lb/>To make men act as senseless wood,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-66" n="66">And chatter in a mistick strain,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-67" n="67">Is a mere farce on flesh &amp; blood,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-68" n="68">And shews some error in the brain.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-69" n="69"><hi rend="italics">18</hi><lb/>He that would thus refine on thee,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-70" n="70">And turn thy Stage into a school,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-71" n="71">The best of Punch shall ever be,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y03-315A-line-72" n="72">And stand confest the greater fool.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
